Etekepari iloshon le moikuape

(
2   Int 
10  .
1  -
19  )


1  Nelo Rehoboam Shekem, eshomo apa Isiraeli pooki Shekem aaitaa ninye olaiguanani. 
2  Ore ake pee ening Yeroboam olayioni le Nebat ina, (Amu eton apa etii Misiri, ine apa neisikaka ailany olaiguanani Solomon) neitoki Yeroboam ashukunye te Misiri. 
3  Neirriwaa ninche olkilikuai aaipotu ninye; ore Yeroboam o eumata oo Siraeli pooki nepuonu aajoki Rehoboam, 
4  “Eiroshiyie apa papaai lino enchata ang oo murto. Ore naa taata nteneneng'a ina kisiaayiare nagol e papaai lino, oina shata nairoishi oo murto natii shumata iyiook, naa aikisiaai iyiook iyie.”


5  Nejoki ninye ninche, “Enchom entung'uayioki too nkolong'i uni, nintokiki aashukunye enatii.” Neaku eshomo iltung'ana.


6  Neitoki olaiguanani Rehoboam aikilikuanishore ilpayiani kituaak apa laa ninche ooitashe te dukuya papaai lenye Solomon, apa eton eishu, nejoki, “Kaa kiutakiki matawaliki ele orere?”


7  Nejoki ninche, “Tenaa iyaku iyie osinka le kulo tung'ana ena olong, nisiaai ninche, nirorie iyie ninche te supatisho tiniwaliki ninche, naa keaku ninche isinkan linono ntarasi.”


8  Kake etanya ninye ina utaroto natuutakita lelo payiani kituaak, neing'oru eutaroto oolbarnot le sirit enye, neitasheyie te dukuya ninye. 
9  Nejoki ninye ninche, “Kaa intae iututu pee kiwaliki ele orere laatiaakitia nanu, ‘Nteneneng'a ina shata oo murto apa natipika papaai lino shumata iyiook?’ ”


10  Nejoki lelo barnot le sirit enye, “Nji shomo tiaki ele orere likijoki ninche, ‘Eiroshiyie apa papaai lino enchata ang oo murto, kake inteneneng'aki iyie iyiook’; nji iyie shomo tiaaki ninche, ‘Ore enkilinta ai naa eisapuk alang empolos e papaai. 
11  Naa ore taata, teneiteleikia papaai intae olchata oiroishi le murt, kaponaa nanu ilo shata linyi loo murto. Eitamio intae papaai too lishien, kaitame nanu intae too nkulupani.’ ”


12  Neaku eewuo Yeroboam tenebo iltung'ana pooki enetii Rehoboam te nkolong e uni, anaa enatejo olaiguanani nejoki olaiguanani ninche, “Enyaaki wootu enatii te nkolong e uni.” 
13  Newalaki olaiguanani iltung'ana te nkitarrikinoto, neany ina utaroto naishoo ilpayiani kituaak. 
14  Neirorie olorere anaa enatuutakitia ninye ilbarnot, ejoki, “Eiroshiyie apa papaai enchata inyi oo murto, naa kaponaa nanu ina shata inyi oo murto; eitamio apa intae papaai too lishien kake kaitame nanu intae too nkulupani.” 
15  Neaku eitu ening olaiguanani olorere, amu embae ena nayaua Olaitoriani pee etum aitabai ororei lenye, apa oiroro Olaitoriani aimunye Ahija le Shilon aliki Yeroboam olayioni le Nebat.


16   Ore ake pee edol Isiraeli pooki aajo eitu ening olaiguanani ninche, newaliki olorere olaiguanani, aajoki,

“Kaa rubata iyiook kiata te Daudi?

Mikiata iyiook enjung'ore to layioni le Yese.

Enchom ilng'oborri linyi intae Israel!

Ng'ura naa taata enkaji ino makewan Daudi.”


17  Neaku eshomo Isiraeli ilng'oborri lenye. Kake eitoria apa Rehoboam iltung'ana loo Siraeli oomanya atua nkanas e Yuda.


18  Neitoki olaiguanani Rehoboam airriwaa Adoram, laa ninye apa olaitasheikinoni le siaai oo nkaik. Nenang iltung'ana pooki loo Siraeli ninye too soito ometua. Neisarisaraki olaiguanani Rehoboam aked engari enye oo mbartan, neisikaki Yerusalem. 
19  Neaku etekepari apa Isiraeli aagilunore enkaji e Daudi ometabaiki ena olong.


20  Ore ake pee ening iltung'ana pooki loo siraeli nchere etorrinyunye Yeroboam, neirriwaa olkilikuai aaipotu ninye meeu eumata, neitaa ninye olaiguanani te shumata Isiraeli pooki. Meetae hoo obo otusujayie enkaji e Daudi, meteleku ake olosho le Yuda.

